data.description: **OPEN HOUSE - 2/3 from 1PM-3PM** Welcome to your future dream home, a charming 3-bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom residence. Nestled in a quiet, friendly, and sought after neighborhood that offer tons of amenities including a large pool, two ponds and plenty of common areas. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area with a wood burning fireplace, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and personalization. The master suite comes with its private bathroom, offering a peaceful retreat after a long day. The additional bedrooms can serve as guest rooms, home offices, or creative spaces, adapting to your lifestyle needs. Stepping outside, you'll discover a generous backyard which includes a creek and a small bridge to connect to the rest of the yard, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or creating a private oasis. As if all of this wasn’t enough, you’re also less than 5 minutes from Woodruff Rd, 5 minutes from I-385, and less than 15 minutes from downtown Greenville and Simpsonville. Amazing location that is hard to beat!
